      "document_id": "computer_vision_project_3_70b116fa78",
      "document_title": "Document Start",
      "chunk_text": "Design and implement a Computer Vision system that solves a real or well-defined\nproblem of your choice. You are free to use classical approaches, deep learning, or a\ncombination of both. You are not required to cover all CV topics — depth and quality on a\nfocused problem is more valuable than a shallow treatment of many techniques.",
      "chunk_index": 2,
      "section_heading": "1. Objective",
      "source_path": null,
      "metadata": {
        "section_id": "sec_3",
        "page_start": "1",
